<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Orden de Fondeo</title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .background-container {
                width: 100%;
                background-image: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/green_degradate.jpg');
                background-size: 100% 100%;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-position: bottom center;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                padding: 30px 0;
            }

            .card-container {
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                background: transparent;
                padding: 20px 35px;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
                position: relative;
            }

            .inner-card {
                background-image: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/white_bg.jpg');
                background-size: cover;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-position: center center;
                padding: 20px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                max-width: 85%;
                margin: auto;
                position: relative;
            }

            .logo {
                height: 27px;
                width: auto;
                margin-right: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 25px;
            }

            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
                color: #5C34F5;
                text-align: left;
                margin: 0;
            }

            .text {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #808285;
            }

            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                background-color: #5C34F5;
                color: #fff;
                border: none;
                padding: 7px 20px;
                text-align: center;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 16px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            .footer {
                text-align: justify;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            .footer p {
                font-size: 10px;
                color: #808285;
            }

            .footer hr {
                border: none;
                border-top: 1px solid #808285;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .card-body-mail {
                background: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/movements.jpg');
                background-size: 38%;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-position: top 30px right 0px;
            }

            .subtitle {
                max-width: 60%;
                font-size: 12px;
                color: #808285;
            }

            .footer-table {
                font-size: 11px;
                color: #808285;
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 25px;
            }

            .details-title {
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 13px;
                margin-top: 25px;
                color: #5C34F5;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .details-table {
                width: 100%;
                font-size: 12px;
            }

            .details-table tr td {
                padding: 8px 0px;
                margin: 0px;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
            }

            .details-table tr td:first-child {
                color: #808285;
                text-align: right;
                padding-right: 25px;
                width: 47%;
            }

            .first-td {
                color: #808285;
                text-align: right;
                padding-right: 25px;
                width: 47%;
            }

            .purple {
                color: #5C34F5;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .btn-api {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .btn-api-format {
                display: inline-block;
                background-color: #5C34F5;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 13px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="background-container">
            <div class="card-container">
                <div class="inner-card">
                    <div class="card-body-mail">
                        <img src="https://viabo.com/production_images/viabo_purple_agil.jpg"
                             alt="Logo de la empresa"
                             class="logo"
                        />
                        <h1 class="title">¡Información de<br>Orden de Fondeo!</h1>
                        <p class="subtitle">
                            Se le ha solicitado el fondeo a una cuenta Viabo con la siguiente información.
                        </p>
                        {% if spei %}
                            <p class="details-title">SPEI: {{ spei }}</p>
                            <hr>
                        {% endif %}

                        {% if urlPayCashFormat|default %}
                            <div class="btn-api">
                                <a class="btn-api-format"
                                   style="color:#f6f6f6"
                                   href="{{ urlPayCashFormat }}"
                                   target="_blank">
                                    Pago en efectivo
                                </a>
                                <br>
                                <a href="{{ urlPayCashDownload }}" target="_blank">Descargar Instrucciones</a>
                            </div>
                            <hr>
                        {% endif %}
                        <table class="details-table">
                            <caption></caption>
                            <th></th>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="fist-td">Monto:</td>
                                <td class="purple">{{ amount }}</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="fist-td">Referencia:</td>
                                <td class="purple">{{ referenceNumber }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                        <p class="footer-table">
                            En caso de enviar los fondos a través de SPEI, por favor agregue la
                            referencia de este correo.
                        </p>
                        {% if urlPayCashFormat|default %}
                            <p class="footer-table">
                                Copie y pegue la siguiente url en su navegador si el botón para pago en efectivo no
                                funciona:
                                <br>
                                <span style="word-break: break-all;">{{ urlPayCashFormat }}</span>
                            </p>
                        {% endif %}
                        <p class="footer-table">
                            Gracias por no responder este correo.
                            <br>
                            Dudas o aclaraciones dirigirse al área correspondiente de la empresa.
                        </p>
                        <hr>
                        <p class="footer-table">ayuda@viabo.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer">
